parameters.name: ダンジョン2(冷たい旋律)

parameters: \n<Prim>Ah, um... Lady Terra, that was a bit too much...

\n<Plum>Did that thing fly off somewhere? This seems like it's going
to be a hassle. Please give me a break.

\n<Plum>Megna and the others got blown away too, you know? You could
at least give us a heads up before doing that.

\n<Plum>Latier and the others got blown away too, you know? You
could at least give us a heads up before doing that.

\n<Plum>Sheika and Barley got blown away too, you know? You could at
least give us a heads up before doing that.
\n<Terra>What... Are you saying it's my fault?

\n<Airia>No, it's the fault of the building made from fragile
materials.

\n<Terra>I'm a succubus, you know? Just because there's a scent of
coagulation crystals, why do I have to go out of my way to
search for them?

\n<Plum>There it is, the 'why should I' argument. The most fruitless
one. You just happened to be nearby, you know? Do you
understand?

\n<Terra>You've been quite provocative since a while ago. It's rare
to find someone who can take such an attitude with me. I'll
spare your life for now.
\n<Terra>Maybe I should do it now after all.

\n<Terra>Rui... Have you returned to your senses already? Impressive.
Just as I expected.
\n<Terra>Ruisham is safe. Don't worry. They're nearby.
\n<Terra>Wanzwas is safe. Don't worry. They're nearby.

\n<Asteria>Can you really call that safe? Under Lady Terra's charm...
they're completely smitten...

\n<Terra>Nfufu♥ I just gave them a little affection♥ Right now
they're in heat because of the charm, but with their magical
power, they'll return to their senses eventually.

\n<Terra>Nfufu♥ I just gave them a little affection♥ It seems they
were already utterly depraved to begin with. You seem to be
the same♥ Fufu♥

\n<Terra>Now that we have a wide and easy place to fight, let's have
some fun♥

\n<Terra>Some other demon will find it eventually. Reinforcements
will come too. Searching through the rubble isn't a
succubus' job.

\n<Rui>Ugh...♥ Ah...♥ (This is beyond anything before...! I must
keep my sanity...!)

\n<Rui>Ah...♥ Ah...♥ (What is this...♥ My sanity is...♥ I need to
calm down...!)

\n<Terra>Oh♥ Despite being so small, it's trying so hard to get hard
and big♥ How cute♥

\n<Terra>In recognition of your courage to confront me, I'll go easy
on you♥ We have the numbers advantage anyway.

\n<Terra>You all. No naughty stuff except for me. I'll fight freely
though.

\n<Terra>Ahh♥ Those eyes♥ My favorite kind of eyes♥ Always keep
looking at me with them♥ Don't let them cloud over so
soon...♥

\n<Rui>Ha... Ugh...♥ (No good...♥ This is...♥ My body is burning
up...♥)

\n<Terra>Oh dear♥ Weren't you going to save Rui? Now all you can
think about is feeling good? I don't like kids who can't try
hard?

\n<Terra>Oh dear♥ Weren't you going to save Wanz? Now all you can
think about is feeling good? I don't like kids who can't try
hard?

\n<Radro>Are you okay, Rui!? That was close... Sorry for being late!
The explosion at the guild made the children cry...!
\n<Rui>Ouch!! What are you doing... huh? What's going on with me...

\n<Ones>Huh? Radro? Radro mom? Huh? What am I doing...? Radro is
mom?

\n<Radro>How many do you think I've disciplined. A punch with love.
Are you awake now?

\n<Radro>But that's not the point! I heard it from the master! Not
the Call Wolf Stone... \C[10]"Coagulation Crystal"!

\n<Radro>They are looking for it! The monster reinforcements are
closing in...! We're out of time!! How about the barrier!?

\n<Radro>Ugh... The barrier is starting to break! This is bad...! We
need to take it somewhere far away, quickly!
\n<Radro>Wait... the wind barrier...! If it's wind, I can help too!

\n<Rui>I see! I've got the situation! There's not much left, but...
I'll use all my magic power!

\n<Ones>I don't really get it, but if we need to put up a barrier,
then that's what we'll do! I don't have much magic power
left, but I'll use it all!
\n<Radro>Gah... haa... haa... Somehow we managed for now...

\n<Rui>This... will only last a few minutes at best... haa...
haa... Damn, they drained more magic power than I thought...

\n<Ones>Cough! Cough! No good... My body, can't muster any
strength... The barrier might not last long...

\n<Rui>Cough... It's okay... It's just that my body can't move
because of magic power depletion... It'll heal if I rest a
bit...

\n<Ones>Oh, seems like they drained more than I thought... Fweeh...
I can't get married now...

\n<Rui>It's okay! I'll carry it outside! Beyond Dri-Ne, beyond
Luma-Re, even further away! I'll show you the speed of a
cat's feet!

\n<Rui>Leave the rest to me! I'll carry it! Beyond Dri-Ne, beyond
Luma-Re, even further away! Don't underestimate a cat's
speed!

\n<Rui>Radro! Thanks for saving me♥ Now, take care of "little
brother"!
\n<Rui>Radro! Thank you! Take care of "little sister" for me!

\n<Rui>"Little brother", huh... sigh. Totally defeated, Rui. Ahh,
now I have two older sisters. Tch.

\n<Ones>"Little sister", huh... Well, whatever. Big bro, do your
best♥ Cough.

\n<Annie>Rui! The town's in trouble! We've evacuated everyone who
can't fight! But there are monsters in the residential area
too...! Damn it! Why is this happening all of a sudden!!

\n<Dodon>Damn it! What the hell is this all of a sudden!! Hey! Rui!
It's an attack! Kill the monsters!!

\n<Dodon>Ahh!? Rui!? Not looking, huh! Maybe they're fighting
somewhere else! You protect the town too!

\n<Dodon>Ahh!? Ones!? Not looking, huh! Maybe they're fighting
somewhere else! You protect the town too!
There's no response. It seems they've already passed away.
There's no response. It seems they've already passed away.
